Parsing config file for zone 0

----------------- Physical Case Definition ( Zone 0 ) -------------------
Compressible Laminar Navier-Stokes' equations.
Mach number: 1.5.
Angle of attack (AoA): 0 deg, and angle of sideslip (AoS): 0 deg.
Reynolds number: 594925. Reference length 0.2.
No restart solution, use the values at infinity (freestream).
Dimensional simulation.
The reference area is 0.15708 m^2.
The semi-span will be computed using the max y(3D) value.
The reference length is 0.2 m.
Reference origin for moment evaluation is (0.1, 0, 0).
Surface(s) where the force coefficients are evaluated: interface.

Surface(s) plotted in the output file: interface.
Input mesh file name: sphere.su2

--------------- Space Numerical Integration ( Zone 0 ) ------------------
Jameson-Schmidt-Turkel scheme (2nd order in space) for the flow inviscid terms.
JST viscous coefficients (2nd & 4th): 0.25, 0.015625.
The method includes a grid stretching correction (p = 0.3).
Average of gradients with correction (viscous flow terms).
Gradient for upwind reconstruction: Green-Gauss.
Gradient for viscous and source terms: Green-Gauss.

--------------- Time Numerical Integration  ( Zone 0 ) ------------------
Unsteady simulation, dual time stepping strategy (second order in time).
Unsteady time step provided by the user (s): 0.0001.
Euler implicit method for the flow equations.
FGMRES is used for solving the linear system.
Using a LU-SGS preconditioning.
Convergence criteria of the linear solver: 1e-06.
Max number of linear iterations: 25.
CFL adaptation. Factor down: 0.5, factor up: 1.5,
                lower limit: 1, upper limit: 5,
                acceptable linear residual: 0.001.
Courant-Friedrichs-Lewy number:        5

------------------ Convergence Criteria  ( Zone 0 ) ---------------------
Maximum number of solver subiterations: 100.
Maximum number of physical time-steps: 200.
Begin convergence monitoring at iteration 5.
Residual minimum value: 1e-4.
Cauchy series min. value: 1e-10.
Number of Cauchy elements: 100.
Begin windowed time average at iteration 9999.
Begin time convergence monitoring at iteration 9999.
Time cauchy series min. value: 0.001.
Number of Cauchy elements: 10.

-------------------- Output Information ( Zone 0 ) ----------------------
File writing frequency: 
